::DeathScythe::

DeathScythe moves forward to where his scanners reported Lunarpine was, the 
assassin keeping his gun ready. A few feet from Lunarpine, DeathScythe comes 
to a stop, transferring his gun to his left hand and pulling out a dagger 
with his right.

He fires the gun in Lunarpine's direction.
